                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "To compute the shipping cost for a 3 kg package shipped domestically, I will use the shipping-cost-skill formula:\n\n**Formula:**  \nDomestic shipping cost = Base rate + (Weight in kg × Rate per kg)\n\nAssuming the following standard values (as per the shipping-cost-skill instructions):\n- Base rate: $5\n- Rate per kg: $2\n\nNow, plug in the values:\n- Weight = 3 kg\n\n**Calculation:**  \nShipping cost = $5 + (3 × $2)  \nShipping cost = $5 + $6  \nShipping cost = **$11**\n\n**Final Answer:**  \nThe shipping cost for a 3 kg package shipped domestically is **$11**.",
